## Documentation

- **Per-server README** (`servers/<name>/README.md`): Tools list, config, env vars, Cursor/Claude Desktop setup.
- **Global README** (`README.md`): Add the new server to the Servers table and Quick Start example after every service add.

---

## Checklist for New Servers

- [ ] `README.md` at server root (tools, config, Cursor config)
- [ ] Update global `README.md` — add server to Servers table
- [ ] `config.json` at server root with mcp + api sections
- [ ] `src/config.ts` loading config, env overrides, `getMCPConfig()` export
- [ ] One API / domain per server
- [ ] Tools in `src/mcp/tools/*Tools.ts` with schema + execute
- [ ] `MCPServerConfig` from env
- [ ] Stdio and HTTP transports selectable via `MCP_TRANSPORT`
- [ ] `/health` and `/mcp` on HTTP
- [ ] Session handling for HTTP (`Mcp-Session-Id`)
- [ ] Tool responses as `{ content: [{ type: 'text', text }] }`
- [ ] Exhaustive switch on tool name, throw for unknown
- [ ] `initialize` / `cleanup` for tools with external deps
- [ ] Logging: connection, request, tool call, session init/close
